--more questions about security and Declarative Pipeline and fewer questions about Freestyle jobs


Certified Jenkins Engineer
The questions reflect the capabilities of the out-of-the-box standard installation of the product, including the Suggested Plugins. 
You may also be asked a few questions about the functionality and uses of other popular plugins.

60 multiple-choice questions
90 minutes allowed to complete the exam

Certified CloudBees Jenkins Engineer
The exam covers current versions of CloudBees Core with an emphasis on features that are available on both traditional platforms and modern cloud platorms

90 multiple-choice questions
60 questions about Jenkins and CloudBees Jenkins Distribution features
30 additional questions about CloudBees Core features


Exam Topics
-Jenkins Fundamentals
-Jenkins Administration
